               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of Mary, መልክአ፡ ማርያም፡; Image of Jesus Christ, መልክአ፡  ኢየሱስ፡; Image of Arägawi/Zä-Mika'el, መልክዐ፡ አረጋዊ፡ /ዘሚካኤል፡;  Image of Gäbrä Mänfäs Qəddus, መልክአ፡ ገብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡;
                    Image of Michael, መልክአ፡ ሚካኤል፡; Image of Gabriel, መልክአ፡ ገብርኤል፡; Image of Saint George, መልክአ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gə‘əz</textLang>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="3r" to="15v"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4112Salam"/>
                  </msItem>
